                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#182v #183r #183v" facs="184 185"/>
                    Prayer for the Intercession of Mary
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በጸሎታ፡ ወበስእለታ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ <abbr>ት</abbr><ex>ሣሀለነ፡</ex> <abbr>እ</abbr><ex>ግዚአ፡</ex> በትንብልናሃ፡ ወበንጽሐ፡ ሥጋሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ <abbr>ት</abbr><ex>ሣሀለነ፡</ex> <abbr>እ</abbr><ex>ግዚአ፡</ex></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#144r" facs="145"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT2809RepCh93"/>
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ሎዛ፡ ቤተ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ወሬዛ፡ አሞ፡ ሞተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ለቤዛ።</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    Inside front and back covers have square mirror niches
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <desc>
                    <locus from="1v" to="21r" facs="003"/><locus target="#144v #145r #145v" facs="146 147"/>
                      Interlinear commentary has been added to many of the Psalms and the Canticles.
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a6">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#9v" facs="011"/>
                    mentions secondary owners Gäbrä Kidan (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብረ፡ ኪዳን፡</foreign>), Gäbrä Śǝllase (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign>), Wäldä Sämaʿǝt (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ሰማዕት፡</foreign>), Wälättä Maryam (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>), and Wälättä ʾIyäsus (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#31r" facs="032"/>
                    later text written in red ink. Sections of the text are illegible due to water damage
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#74r" facs="075"/>
                    The midpoint of the Psalms is marked with a small ornamental band in red and black ink and the text <foreign xml:lang="gez">መንፈቅ፡</foreign> ʿhalfʾ
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#182v" facs="184"/>
                    a curse on anyone who steals the book
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a7">
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    <locus target="#182v" facs="184"/>
                    mentions an owner, Wälättä Bǝrhan (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ፡ ብርሃን፡</foreign>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#9 #56" facs="010 057"/>
                    red string stitched into fore edge as navigation system
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <desc>
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#6v #15r #16v #17r #17v" facs="008 016 018 019"/>, etc.);
                      lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#35r #35v #57r #59v #155r" facs="036 037 058 061 156"/>, etc.);
                      lines of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#12v #14r #96r" facs="014 015 097"/>);
                      erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#25r"/>);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#6v #9v #53r #53v #54r" facs="008 011 054 055"/>, etc.).
                    </desc>
                    </item>
